621
00:26:31,080 --> 00:26:32,570
and notified a general

622
00:26:32,610 --> 00:26:33,410
of Wu State.

623
00:26:34,860 --> 00:26:36,190
This general of Wu State

624
00:26:36,290 --> 00:26:37,380
thought his people

625
00:26:37,420 --> 00:26:38,220
