626
00:26:38,720 --> 00:26:39,750
So, in a fit of anger,

627
00:26:39,750 --> 00:26:41,920
he got an army to launch an attack on Chu State.

628
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:42,900
In the end, it became

629
00:26:42,900 --> 00:26:44,960
