00:39:17,680 --> 00:39:18,900
When your brother becomes an official,

872
00:39:18,900 --> 00:39:20,830
I will ask him to pay it back for you.

873
00:39:24,110 --> 00:39:24,990
As for the rest,

874
00:39:28,230 --> 00:39:29,910
we can't shortchange you.

875
00:39:48,900 --> 00:39:50,770
When one grows up,

876
00:39:57,050 --> 00:39:58,910
one has to go on their own journey.

877
00:40:35,070 --> 00:40:38,600
[Recommended Students]

878
00:40:44,310 --> 00:40:45,590
The peanuts are not sold out yet.

879
00:40:45,590 --> 00:40:46,990
Why are you sitting here?

880
00:40:49,990 --> 00:40:51,980
The day before yesterday, at the fields,

881
00:40:51,980 --> 00:40:54,310
I advised your grandfather to make a decision.

882
00:40:54,310 --> 00:40:55,440
I originally wanted

883
00:40:55,590 --> 00:40:57,910
to let your grandpa agree to you splitting from the family.

884
00:40:57,910 --> 00:40:59,350
I didn't expect Mr. Lian

885
00:40:59,880 --> 00:41:01,640
to think of divorce.

886
00:41:03,160 --> 00:41:04,090
I was complacent

887
00:41:04,650 --> 00:41:05,580
and went too far.

888
00:41:07,510 --> 00:41:09,240
I thought something happened.

889
00:41:09,900 --> 00:41:11,360
You're quite thoughtful.

890
00:41:12,230 --> 00:41:13,140
If it weren't for you,

891
00:41:13,140 --> 00:41:14,330
my grandparents wouldn't have forced my father

892
00:41:14,330 --> 00:41:15,130
to this point,

893
00:41:15,200 --> 00:41:17,460
and my father wouldn't have fought back.

894
00:41:17,630 --> 00:41:18,890
It's all thanks to you.

895
00:41:24,500 --> 00:41:26,410
You've been staring at the ancestral hall.

896
00:41:26,410 --> 00:41:27,740
What are you looking at?

897
00:41:28,910 --> 00:41:30,680
To have an ancestral memorial tablet

898
00:41:30,680 --> 00:41:32,150
in the ancestral hall means that

899
00:41:32,150 --> 00:41:34,010
one must have made achievements.

900
00:41:34,750 --> 00:41:35,640
Although I spoke uprightly and straightforwardly

901
00:41:35,640 --> 00:41:37,040
in front of your grandpa,

902
00:41:37,530 --> 00:41:38,320
I don't think

903
00:41:38,340 --> 00:41:39,740
he was completely wrong.

904
00:41:40,590 --> 00:41:41,390
In this world,

905
00:41:41,940 --> 00:41:43,140
the imperial examination

906
00:41:43,140 --> 00:41:44,870
is the only way out for farmers.

907
00:41:46,240 --> 00:41:48,370
It's understandable that he's always

908
00:41:48,390 --> 00:41:50,120
looking out for Uncle Shouren.

909
00:41:51,310 --> 00:41:52,570
It's understandable?

910
00:41:54,420 --> 00:41:56,820
Even if everyone acknowledges this logic,

911
00:41:57,020 --> 00:41:58,480
it's still unreasonable.

912
00:41:59,940 --> 00:42:01,070
In the future world,

913
00:42:01,470 --> 00:42:03,990
people will not be discriminated based on their profession.

914
00:42:03,990 --> 00:42:05,320
Everyone will be equal.

915
00:42:07,100 --> 00:42:08,100
The future world?

916
00:42:09,180 --> 00:42:09,980
That's right.

917
00:42:11,430 --> 00:42:14,460
We have to always look forward.

918
00:42:15,570 --> 00:42:17,080
There will come a day when

919
00:42:17,190 --> 00:42:18,190
everyone is equal

920
00:42:18,990 --> 00:42:20,650
and can live and work in peace.

921
00:43:06,030 --> 00:43:07,430
Why are you looking at me?

922
00:43:10,970 --> 00:43:12,060
You look so happy.

923
00:43:12,710 --> 00:43:13,420
Have you thought through

924
00:43:13,420 --> 00:43:15,310
how you're going to split from the family?

925
00:43:15,310 --> 00:43:17,170
What else is there to think about?

926
00:43:17,420 --> 00:43:18,680
Royalty and powerful officials

927
00:43:18,680 --> 00:43:20,860
divide their property and family businesses.

928
00:43:20,860 --> 00:43:22,520
Although your family is poor,

929
00:43:23,070 --> 00:43:24,580
you still have some family business

930
00:43:24,580 --> 00:43:25,500
and fields.

931
00:43:26,830 --> 00:43:28,630
But with your grandma's temper,

932
00:43:29,030 --> 00:43:31,230
she wouldn't give it to you for nothing.

933
00:43:32,350 --> 00:43:33,810
Why didn't I think of that?

934
00:43:34,910 --> 00:43:36,620
My parents won't fight for anything more

935
00:43:36,620 --> 00:43:38,220
and Seven is still too young.

936
00:43:38,380 --> 00:43:40,420
I’m the only one who can talk about it.

937
00:43:40,420 --> 00:43:41,430
How can I win against Uncle Shouyi's family

938
00:43:41,430 --> 00:43:42,210
and Grandma?

939
00:43:44,100 --> 00:43:46,260
Splitting from the family is such a huge matter.

940
00:43:46,260 --> 00:43:48,660
Does Aunt's maternal family know about it?

941
00:43:52,940 --> 00:43:54,180
Are you saying

942
00:43:55,380 --> 00:43:57,310
I should call for reinforcements?

943
00:44:02,620 --> 00:44:08,280
[Mission: 1,000 taels of gold]

944
00:44:02,620 --> 00:44:08,280
[Income (selling garlic peanuts): 78 taels]

945
00:44:02,620 --> 00:44:08,280
